-- Husky Energy Probing Platform Fire Cause Off Newfoundland
-- B y   J e s s i c a   R e s n i c k - A u l t
-- 2012-08-08T11:21:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-08/husky-energy-probing-platform-fire-cause-off-newfoundland.html
Husky Energy Inc. (HSE)  is investigating a
fire in a pump room on its SeaRose oil platform off the coast of
Newfoundland.  The fire was noticed shortly after 5 p.m. yesterday,
according to a Canadian Press report. There were no injuries and
no evacuation was necessary. The fire was contained in the pump
room.  Damage is still being assessed, according to the release.
The platform shut for maintenance this summer, and is not
currently producing oil.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jessica Resnick-Ault at 
 jresnickault@bloomberg.net  